{"id": "1243938410411065406", "channel_id": "1242853778714132582", "type": 0, "author_id": "761032725666725888", "author_name": "dittoqwq", "author_bot": false, "content": "菜式真的靠脑补，请见谅。其实我认为赫伯特更像只羊？就西方那种羊，好像有恶魔的意思", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T14:47:08.300000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1242853778714132582", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿尔比诺x你  同人文 （3）", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1242759499010412605"]}
{"id": "1243938918928482337", "channel_id": "1242853778714132582", "type": 0, "author_id": "761032725666725888", "author_name": "dittoqwq", "author_bot": false, "content": "罗杰斯有点刀子，因为以前小时候被母亲灌药，就觉得他喉咙可能会有点受损", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T14:49:09.540000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1242853778714132582", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "阿尔比诺x你  同人文 （3）", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359790249332756", "1242759499010412605"]}
